      "created_at": "2023-07-01T16:41:40.043Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I want to point out, that we made a change to fit the HR mode on the screen.  That if a person uses resistance mode instead of slope mode they should go to settings now and switch it to resistance mode.</p>\n<p>When you switch to resistance mode it looks like this.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd_2_574x500.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"rimg6IfWybTWESTiP3a0wG8nxbn\" width=\"574\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd_2_574x500.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd_2_861x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/bf4df9df9892befb59b77e537980d6c865c351cd_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1006\u00d7876 49.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
