      "created_at": "2023-07-03T01:57:33.115Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Top of the day<br>\nWas doing tabata thing, they s_ck, in egr mode and in the on part[350+] for 20 sec was spot on, but in the off part[10 seconds] it never released to the recovery wattage. Is this common? Is it better to do these in a different mode, restitance or slope?<br>\nAnd how does slope work?<br>\nGo from there and jabber later</p>",
